<item>
            <title>[LU-1242] Explanation of &quot;select flavor null&quot; and &quot;mount.lustre: addmntent: Invalid argument:&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1242</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I am just looking for an explanation of the above messages. The mount.lustre error occurs on both server targets and client mounts. The &quot;select flavor null&quot; message appears on the MDS when the client mounts the file system. They appear to be informational only since they aren&apos;t associated with any error messages. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Feel free to close the ticket after responding.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>TOSS 2.0 Operating system</environment>
