                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="31769" author="green" created="Wed, 21 Mar 2012 13:56:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The addmntent message comes from a failed call to addmntent() that is supposed to add the mount entry to /etc/mtab. I imagine the reason must be because you have /etc/mtab as a symlink somewhere non-writeable (like /proc/mounts).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="31632" author="adilger" created="Wed, 21 Mar 2012 00:18:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The &quot;select flavor null&quot; message is removed in 2.2, but I&apos;m not sure what the addmntenr message is from. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
